\begin{aligned} S_{\triangle PAB} &=\frac{1}{3} S_{ABC}, \\ S_{\triangle PAC} &=\frac{1}{4} S_{ABC}. \end{aligned}
\] 由面积公式得: \[
\begin{aligned} S_{\triangle PAB} &=\frac{1}{2} \cdot PB \cdot AP=\frac{1}{3} S_{ABC}, \\ S_{\triangle PAC} &=\frac{1}{2} \cdot PC \cdot AP=\frac{1}{4} S_{ABC}. \end{aligned}
\] 所以: \[
\begin{aligned} PB \cdot AP &=\frac{1}{6} S_{ABC}, \\ PC \cdot AP &=\frac{1}{8} S_{ABC}. \end{aligned}
\] 由于 $\overrightarrow{AP}=\lambda \overrightarrow{AB}+\mu \overrightarrow{AC}$, 所以: \[
\begin{aligned} PB &=\frac{\lambda}{\lambda+1} AB, \\ PC &=\frac{\mu}{\lambda+1} AC. \end{aligned}
\] 因此: \[
\begin{aligned} \frac{\lambda}{\lambda+1} AB \cdot AP &=\frac{1}{6} S_{ABC}, \\ \frac{\mu}{\lambda+1} AC \cdot AP &=\frac{1}{8} S_{ABC}. \end{aligned}
\] 联立解得: \[
\begin{aligned} \lambda &=\frac{1}{5}, \\ \mu &=\frac{1}{3}. \end{aligned}
\] 故答案为: $\lambda=\frac{1}{5}$; $\mu=\frac{1}{3}$.

